an express scotti was recognized as one of the “marketing top  under ” by advertising age in  and was one of  marketers named as “internationalists” by international magazine in  he is a member of the board of directors of the ana and ad council a native of argentina scotti earned a bachelor of arts degree in advertising and marketing communications from the university of management and social sciences in buenos aires diego scotti job titlecmo companyverizon events tue ●  am driving diverse thought the new roles  responsibilities of clients and agencies see full  calendar speaking with antonio lucio global chief marketing  communication officer hp inc  event aline santos farhat svp global marketing unilever  event view featured speakers news announcements sign up to receive the latest announcements seminars  speakers special events and more buy pass about aw partnership subscribe contact  west rd street new york ny       email privacy policy  terms and conditions diego scotti executive profile  biography  bloomberg july    pm et diversified telecommunication services company overview of verizon communications inc snapshotpeople  overviewboard memberscommittees executive profile diego scotti chief marketing officer and executive vice president verizon communications incagetotal calculated compensationthis person is connected to  board members in  different organizations across  different industriessee board relationships background mr diego scotti serves as chief marketing officer and executive vice president of verizon nederland bv mr scotti has been the chief marketing officer of verizon communications inc since october   and serves as its executive vice president he is responsible for linking the innovations of verizon’s product team to the customerfocused operations of the business units to build the verizon global brand create consumer awareness and advocacy and drive customer  preference for the brand through all channels every day he oversees the global management of verizon’s brand including consumer insights digital marketing creative development and agency management marketing effectiveness social responsibility sponsorships media and employee communications given the demonstrated power of big data and digital marketing he also oversees the leveraging of verizon’s current capabilities to help build its global brand he has a wealth of experience creating and developing innovative marketing strategies and unique customer experiences he joined verizon in october  mr scotti served as the chief marketing officer and senior vice president at j crew group inc since october  he was responsible for all retail and direct marketing projects for j crew and madewell the brand created by j crew in  prior to j crew he oversaw marketing for several print and digital media brands at conde nast publications he served as an executive director of marketing for vogue prior to vogue he served  years at american express as head of global advertising and brand management and served several other domestic and international positions mr scotti has been a director of the advertising council inc ad council since october   he is a member of the board of directors of the ana he has been recognized one of the marketing top  under  by advertising age in  and one of  marketers named internationalists by international magazine in  he earned a bachelor of arts degree in advertising and marketing communications from the university of management and social sciences in buenos airesread full background corporate headquarters  avenue of the americasnew york new york united statesphone fax  board members memberships presentdirectorthe advertising council inc education ba universidad de ciencias empresariales y sociales other affiliations j crew group incthe advertising council incverizon nederland bvuniversidad de ciencias empresariales y sociales annual compensation there is no annual compensation data available stocks options there is no stock options data